Jonathan M Miller

...Who?

I'm Jonathan Miller.

I write software.

I build things.

I volunteer.

I run trails.

I go places.

I tell stories.

I solve problems.


If you're looking at this site, there's a pretty good chance that you either know me or you want to know me. Or, better yet, you're just a curious reader at the end of a trail of purple hyperlinks.

In any case, I'm glad you're here and I hope you'll take a look at the work I've done and the stories I've told.
